  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>These goggles feature highly reflective lenses. While wearing the goggles, you gain a +3 item bonus to visual Perception checks and to saving throws against visual effects.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong><span class=\"action-glyph\">R</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature within 60 feet targets you with a visual effect</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You turn your head to reflect aspects of the triggering effect back at its creator. The creature must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:40] save as it becomes disoriented by this reflection. On a failure, the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 1} (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 2} on a critical failure). The creature is temporarily immune for 1 hour.</p>"
